    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Die sextodecimo mensis novenbris, ind(icione) VI, in <rs key="#Vici">vico</rs> qui vocatur
                        <placeName key="#Vici" ref="#places/4607">Rovoreto</placeName>, infra sacrato <rs key="#Churches">ecclesie</rs> 
                        <orgName key="#Churches">Sancte Marię</orgName>. Dum adessent <persName
                            key="#Count"><name ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName> <rs key="#Count">comes</rs>
                        <placeName key="#Cities" ref="#places/80">Ferrarie</placeName> et Rotegerius Regiensis iudex et 
                        <persName><name ref="Teodericus de Canossa">Tedericus</name></persName> de <placeName ref="#places/2415">Canossa</placeName> et Clareto
                        [clerico], missi domini Gotofredi ducis et cum eis residentibus iudicibus
                        Albertus Boloniensis iudex, Segnoreto Ficariensis, Wido iudex et
                        G(re)g(orius) iudex Ferrariensis et Liuzius causidicus Ravenas et Stephanus
                        et Pet(rus) Michael(is), Wido filius condam Frederici, Zochulo filio
                        Rofredi, Iohannes de Tebaldo, <persName key="#Tabellio"><name ref="Iohannes">Iohannes</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Tabellio">tabellio</rs>, Adam de Demizo, Ugo de
                        Guncedruda, Fantone, Alberto de Papia, Bonofantino, Iohannes de Epp[o],
                        Riperto, Gibulo et alii plures adstantes et residentes et me presente
                        Iohanne tabellione Ferrarie; in mea et suprascriptorum presentia tenens
                        virgam in manu sua <rs key="#Abbots">ab[ba]s</rs> <persName key="#Abbots" ref="#people/1596">Mainardus</persName> 
                        <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterii</rs> <orgName key="#Monasteries #Cows" ref="#juridical_persons/1460">Sanctę Marię in 
                            <placeName key="#Cows" ref="#places/4179">Pomposia</placeName></orgName> cum
                        <persName
                            key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities"><name ref="Oddo">Oddone</name></persName> 
                        <rs key="#Advocatus_of_other_public_authorities">avocatore</rs> suo misit in manus Mart(ino) de presbitero Petro et Alberti
                        de Presbitero et presbiteri Walterii, Iohanni de Petro, Urselli de Petro
                        Grosso et Dominici gastaldi dicens: ‘Ego remitto vobis et per vos omnibus
                        aliis obligationem et wadimonium de rapina <rs key="#Cows">boum centum L</rs> unde usque modo
                        obligati fuistis ad meum monasterium in persona suprascripti advocatoris
                        ea fide et condicione ut quicquit de suprascripta rapina in emendatum
                        remansit, reddere debeatis ab hinc usque ad festivitatem sancti Andręe
                        prope venientis et ut nullam molestiam vel offensionem a modo facere
                        debeatis meo monasterio neque mihi neque successoribus meis de bonis
                        omnibus que predictum monasterium nunc abet et detinet et unde investicionem
                        accepi secundum precepti et iudicati seriem, quę <rs key="#Landed_possessions">omnia</rs> posita sunt inter
                        <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/4196">Padum</placeName> et 
                        <placeName key="#Landed_possessions" ref="#places/3588">Sandalum</placeName> ita videlicet, ut si hec omnia non observaveritis, in
                        eadem obligatione permaneatis. Factum est hoc sub die, mense et indic(ione)
                        suprascripta. + Ego Iohannes in Dei nomine tabellio huic pagine refutationis
                        manus mea subscripsi.</ab>
